Django Hello World Project

Installing:

Requirments: *bower* front-end package-manager

```
    git clone https://github.com/TraMZzz/angular-backend
    cd angular-backend
    make install
    make bower-install
```

Running:

Start django backend  

```
    cd angular-backend
    make run
```
  
Open URL in browser locally: http://127.0.0.1:8000/ 


### Testing:

Installing Karma test-runner:  

Requirements: *nodejs* & *npm*

```
    cd angular-backend
    make test-install
```

Runing test

```
    cd angular-backend
    make karma-test
```
